                <Header>Pardons / Commutations</Header>
                <Paragraph>The Department of Justice's Office of the Pardon Attorney maintains a list of Presidential pardons and commutations on its "Clemency Recipients" web page. The list starts with pardons and commutations that President Richard M. Nixon granted and ends with those that were granted by President Donald J. Trump. .</Paragraph>
